@page "/about"
@inject NavigationManager NavManager

    <PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="home-hero">
    <h1>Score Counter</h1>
    <p>Keep track of scores — simple, fast, and stylish. Perfect for games, competitions, and after work.</p>
</div>

<div class="home-features">
    <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>Create Match</h3>
        <p>Create a match in seconds. Choose players, starting score, target score (Max Score), and rules — highest or lowest wins.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">👥</div>
        <h3>Invite Players</h3>
        <p>Share the match link or scan the QR code. Everyone sees the scores and history in real time via SignalR.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">📊</div>
        <h3>Real-Time Scoring</h3>
        <p>Update scores with one click (-1, -5, +1, +5) or enter any custom amount. Changes sync instantly to all devices.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">📋</div>
        <h3>Score History</h3>
        <p>Every score change is tracked with timestamp. View history grouped by player — who scored what and when.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">🏆</div>
        <h3>Results & Draw</h3>
        <p>End the match to see final standings. If two players have the same top score, it's a draw — shown clearly with both names.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">🔄</div>
        <h3>Clone & Reset</h3>
        <p>Clone a match to keep current scores. Reset to start fresh with the same players and settings.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">📱</div>
        <h3>QR Code Sharing</h3>
        <p>Generate a QR code for any match. Others scan it with their phone to join instantly — no typing needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">🌙</div>
        <h3>Dark Mode</h3>
        <p>Toggle between light and dark theme. Works on mobile, tablet, and desktop with responsive design.</p>
    </div>
</div>
